name: Fotofolio postcard pack: 'Places to Eat'
description:
A fotofolio of 10 postcards on the theme of 'Places to Eat', from photographer Kay Westhues. Each pack of 4" x 6" cards contains 10 different images from her Fourteen Places to Eat photo project.

These cards have a thick 16pt, sustainably sourced paper stock, with a glossy laminate finish one one side. The other side is lightly coated with a faint satin finish, making it easier to write your own message. The paper stock is also acid and lignin free.
